ct."},"I like to work with people who…":{emoji:"🤝",helperText:"Consider the qualities and characteristics you value in colleagues, and how they contribute to a positive work environment, collaboration, and project success."},"I want to work in a company that…":{emoji:"🏢",helperText:"Consider company aspects that align with your values, goals, and preferences, and reflect on the environment and culture that would best support your growth and well-being."},"At work, I’m best at…":{emoji:"🏅",helperText:"Consider your unique strengths, skills, and abilities in your professional life and reflect on experiences or accomplishments that demonstrate these qualities."},"When I’m not working, I enjoy…":{emoji:"❤️",helperText:"Consider hobbies and interests you engage in during free time, and reflect on their contribution to well-being, personal growth, and work-life balance."},"Right now, I’m learning…":{emoji:"🧑‍🏫",helperText:"Consider new skills or experiences you’re engaging in, reflecting on your learning motivation, its relation to personal or professional goals, and progress made."},"In my next job, it’s important that…":{emoji:"💼",helperText:"Reflect on essential factors for satisfaction and success in your next role, using past experiences to understand preferences, goals, and priorities."},"I’m making a career change because…":{emoji:"🧭",helperText:"Consider reasons for your career change, reflecting on experiences, goals, and priorities, and how your current path may not meet your needs or aspirations."},"My proudest accomplishment is…":{emoji:"🙌",helperText:"Consider meaningful experiences, achievements, or milestones, reflecting on challenges overcome, personal growth, and lessons learned."},"I am passionate about contributing to a positive work culture by…":{emoji:"🤗",helperText:"Consider actions and behaviors you bring to foster a positive work environment, reflecting on past experiences, personal values, and your impact on colleagues and atmosphere."},"In the next few years, I hope to…":{emoji:"🎯",helperText:"Consider personal and professional aspirations for upcoming years, reflecting on desired growth, exciting challenges, and milestones to achieve."},"In my current role, I’m missing the opportunity to…":{emoji:"✋",helperText:"Consider unfulfilled experiences or aspects in your current position, reflecting on personal and professional goals, values, and preferences not fully realized in your role."},"The most impactful thing I’ve worked on is…":{emoji:"😇",helperText:"Consider impactful projects or accomplishments and reflect on challenges overcome, value created, and lessons learned during the process."},"I love solving problems that are…":{emoji:"🤔",helperText:"Consider challenges that excite and motivate you, reflecting on skills, interests, and values, and their alignment with the problems you enjoy tackling."},"I bring creativity to my projects by…":{emoji:"🧑‍🎨",helperText:"Consider techniques used to infuse projects with creativity and reflect on your unique perspective, experiences, and skills that contribute to creative problem-solving."},"In my next role, I hope to expand my knowledge in…":{emoji:"🧠",helperText:"Consider areas or skills you’d like to develop in your next role, reflecting on personal and professional goals, current expertise, and benefits to career growth."},"I bring a unique perspective to my work because…":{emoji:"👋",helperText:"Consider unique qualities, experiences, or characteristics and reflect on how they contribute to problem-solving, collaboration, and generating innovative ideas."},"My favorite thing about a previous role I had was…":{emoji:"😍",helperText:"Consider enjoyable aspects of a past job and reflect on what made it stand out, aligning with your values, interests, and professional goals."},"A side project I built that I’m proud of is…":{emoji:"💡",helperText:"Consider aspects of a personal project developed outside your primary career and reflect on what made it special, aligning 